ecause the failure (email not reaching inbox) is an infrastructure concern requiring real email delivery testing. Integration-level mocks would hide delivery failures. Agentic is not required—summary accuracy is tested separately.","level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.02,"Integration":0.05,"System":0.7,"Agentic":0.15,"Workflow":0.08}},{"behavior_id":5,"description":"When the email delivery service is unreachable, the generated report is saved to a local file and delivery is retried on the next scheduled run.","minimum_level":"Integration","justification":"This is about error recovery across module boundaries. The failure mode spans two time periods: first run (email fails, report must persist), second run (scheduler must detect persisted report and retry). Catching this requires multiple modules coordinating: report generator → error handling → file persistence → scheduler detection → retry logic. A unit test of 'save to file' alone wouldn't catch if the scheduler never detects the saved file; a unit test of 'scheduler retry logic' alone wouldn't catch if the report isn't persisted. The integration must work end-to-end.","test_description":"Mock the email service to raise an exception (simulating unreachable service). Run the report generator and verify it catches the email error. Verify the generated report is saved to a local persistence directory with a status marker (e.g., delivery_status='failed'). Simulate the next scheduled run by creating/running a scheduler task that scans the persistence directory. Verify the scheduler detects the saved report and attempts retry. Optionally, mock email to succeed on the second run and verify the report is marked as delivered or cleaned up.","plan_consistent":true,"plan_consistent_note":"Integration is the minimum because the failure depends on error handling, persistence, and scheduler logic working together. A unit test of one piece wouldn't catch if the handoff between modules fails. System-level is unnecessary without testing real filesystem or real scheduler service.","level_probabilities":{"Unit":0.15,"Integration":0.7,"System":0.1,"Agentic":0.03,"Workflow":0.02}}]},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12428,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":12428},"output_tokens":4,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"a804c03a-dea2-435c-86c6-d28b8ee7b937","uuid":"8d1dd977-630e-4ac9-8fd3-67cbe1c860a5"}
